
#sample-utilities
  h4 Utilities

  p.
    Utilities are classes that can help you to easily show up your data
    or content in a beatiful way. It can be used combined with other
    available classes.

  h5 Text alignment

  .grid

    .row
      .col.md-5.sm-12
        p.align-left This is left aligned

        .code-sample
          pre.prettyprint.lang-html.
            &lt;p class="align-left" &gt; ... &lt;/p&gt;

        br

        p.align-center This is center aligned

        .code-sample
          pre.prettyprint.lang-html.
            &lt;p class="align-center" &gt; ... &lt;/p&gt;

        br

      .col.sm-12.md-5.md-offset-1

        p.align-right This is right aligned

        .code-sample
          pre.prettyprint.lang-html.
            &lt;p class="align-right" &gt; ... &lt;/p&gt;

        br

        p.align-justify.
          This is justified. This is justified. This is justified. This is justified.
          This is justified. This is justified. This is justified. This is justified.

        .code-sample
          pre.prettyprint.lang-html.
            &lt;p class="align-justify" &gt; ... &lt;/p&gt;

    .row
      .col

        table
          thead
            tr
